plot: As Ryan's Kryptonite wound worsens, it hinders her capabilities as Batwoman. Efforts to copy the Desert Rose serum endanger Mary and Cmdr Kane. Meanwhile Alice's reunion with someone from Coryana presents unexpected complications.

As the radiation from the Kryptonite bullet catches up with Ryan, Batwoman takes on an opponent who is also seeking the Desert Rose serum so that he can cure the blood cancer in all his brain. Meanwhile Alice is torn between killing Ocean to recover Kate - and sparing her former lover.—Gislef
